### Enhancements

* Depend on standalone conda-index instead of bundled indexing code. (#4690)

### Bug fixes

* <news item>

### Deprecations

* Inline `conda index` logic is pending deprecation. `conda-build` still provides
  `conda-index` a.k.a. `conda index` CLI, but uses standalone
  `conda-index` during builds.
* Prefer the [standalone conda-index package](https://conda.github.io/conda-index/),
  instead of `conda-build index` or `conda index`, to use faster indexing code.

